Spencer Mansion
Zork++
Welcome to the Spencer Mansion...
You're a member of an elite special forces team that was sent to investigate
this mysterious estate in the mountains after a bizarre incident wiped out an
entire nearby city. Most of your teammates were killed in an ambush soon after
arriving in a helicopter, except for the pilot, who was forced to leave you
behind and land elsewhere. In the ensuing chaos, you fled inside the mansion.
Your mission is to find a way to contact your missing teammate while exploring
the mansion, so you both can escape safely from this horrible nightmare
together.
